name: Park Tool CN-10 Professional Cable/Housing Cutters
description: The right tool for the job does the job right. These high-quality cutters are engineered specifically to use on bike cables and housing, including hard-to-cut index housing.Cold-forged, heat-treated steel handles and jaws for strength.Ergonomic rubber handles.Precision-ground jaws for a clean cut.Built-in crimper for cable end caps, and a forming hole for reforming housing ends and ferrules.Wire latch holds handles together in storage.
